field.description: Landing/Entrance Page (first 'Page View' event) of a Session.
field.label: Behavior Landing Page
field.name: sessions.landing_page
field.sql:
(select coalesce(regexp_extract((select value.string_value from UNNEST(event_params) where key = "page_location"),r"(?:.*?[\.][^\/]*)([\/][^\?]+)"),'/')
          from UNNEST(sessions.event_data) as event_history
          where event_history.sl_key = (sessions.sl_key) and event_history.page_view_rank = 1 limit 1)
